
            Video
            From Russia Without Love? - a Newsbeat documentary
            Tensions are high between Russia and the UK right now.Russia has been accused of a lot - everything from poisoning spies to peddling fake news and trying to influence elections.So what do Russians think of Britain? Radio 1 Newsbeat's Will Chalk and Matt Wareham spent a week finding out.This video is not available through the BBC app but you can view the documentary on iPlayer by clicking here. Listen to Newsbeat live at 12:45 and 17:45 every weekday on BBC Radio 1 and 1Xtra - if you miss us you can listen back here. 
                
                        22 Nov 2018
                    
                
        
